YNaija bụ ikpo okwu na-ebipụta ihe n'ịntanetị nke Naijiria, nke Chude Jideonwo na Adebola Williams nke RED Africa media group guzobere
YNaija malitere na Mee 2010 site na ndị na-ede akwụkwọ akụkọ na akụkọ dị iche iche
Ọ na-enye akụkọ, ọdịnaya mbụ ma na-ekpuchi ndọrọ ndọrọ ọchịchị, azụmahịa, ntụrụndụ, gburugburu ebe obibi, teknụzụ, mgbasa ozi a ma ama, ụdị ndụ, ọdịbendị, ihe ọchị na ndụ dị mma.
N'ọnwa Julaị n'afọ 2012, YNaija nọ n'ọkwa # 5 n'elu blọọgụ na mba ahụ, site n'aka CPAfrica.

Akara Y! gụnyekwara ihe ngosi telivishọn, ihe ngosi redio na magazin a na-ebipụta.
Magazin ahụ, Y!, bụ mbipụta kwa ọnwa nke malitere na mbụ dị ka nkeji iri na ise.
Ọ haziri ihe omume gụnyere #Hashtag Party na July 2011, YNaija Black Ball, na ndị ọzọ.
Na mgbakwunye na kọlụm Y! Frontpage nke Ebuka Obi-Uchendu, Tolu Ogunlesi, Kathleen Ndongmo, Japheth J

Omojuwa, Ayo Sogunro na Akintunde Oyebode, enwere ọtụtụ ndị ọzọ na-enyere aka na Y! Politico, SuperBlogger na 30 Days, 30 Voices na ndị ọzọ na akwụkwọ akụkọ ahụ, gụnyere Abang Mercy, Subomi Plumptre na Ifeanyi Dike Jr.
N'afọ 2012, ndị guzobere YNaija bụ Chude Jideonwo na Adebola Williams bú ndị a gụnyere  na ndepụta 40 under 40 nke ụlọọrụ BusinessDay.
N'ọnwa Febụwarị afọ 2013, a kpọrọ aha Jideonwo na Williams na Forbes '30 Under 30: Africa's Best Young Entrepreneurs.
Blọọgụ teknụzụ na ụdị ndụ, CPAfrica kpọrọ YNaija blọọgụ nke ise na Naijiria n'afọ 2012.
